Package: vegperiod
Version: 0.2.4
Title: Determine Vegetation Periods of Forest Trees
Authors@R: c(person("Robert", "Nuske", role=c("aut", "cre"), 
             email="robert.nuske@nw-fva.de"))
Author: Robert Nuske
Maintainer: Robert Nuske <robert.nuske@nw-fva.de>
Depends: R (>= 2.15.0)
Imports: methods, utils
Suggests: RCurl, testthat (>= 1.0.0)
Description: Calculate start and end date of vegetation periods based on
  daily average air temperature and the day of the year (DOY). A sum
  of day degrees within vegetation period and functions for reading
  freely accessible meteo data from DWD's ftp-Server are provided on top.
URL: https://www.nw-fva.de/r-pkgs
BugReports: via email to <robert.nuske@nw-fva.de>
Encoding: UTF-8
License: GPL (>= 3)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
NeedsCompilation: no
